00014 /**
00015  * This class is used to change the owner and permissions of a file.
00016  * Set Owner uses java.nio.file.Files.setOwner for cross-platform support.
00017  * Set Permissions attempts to identify the Operating System, using java.nio.file.attribute.AclFileAttributeView for Windows, 
00018  * and java.nio.file.attribute.PosixFileAttributeView for any other.
00019  */
